{"tid":2246421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"王婆婆被国安迫睇嗰套戲....","createTime":"2020-10-17T05:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T06:13:25.000Z","uid":12277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30e5e41178bf584107b9688e57a7876d6c9b3def","tid":2246421,"uid":12277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"係英皇拍<br />\n你仲去佢戲院睇戲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「經常在示威場合舉英國旗、人稱「王婆婆」的王鳳瑤，去年反修例運動期間，8 月 11 日於太古地鐵站最後露面後行踪不明，其後透露於深圳被指涉嫌「尋釁滋事」，先後被扣押於福田拘留所及深圳第三看守所逾月，王鳳瑤今早召開記者會公開經歷。記者會正式開始前，王鳳瑤向鏡頭舉起 &ldquo;Save 12 HK Youths&rdquo;的紙牌，呼籲關注 12 名目前被扣押於鹽田看守所的港人。<br />\n<br />\n記者會直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3dxtaSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3dxtaSo&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=361e48c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3dxtaSo</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖片資料來源：朱凱廸整理王婆婆憶述後發出新聞稿）」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdxJEwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdxJEwn.jpg&h=ff0f8c46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEDs6bo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEDs6bo.jpg&h=7cef7393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31ee933128b15fef77e557df777d64c03635f27f","tid":2246421,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76da10ef11b411b31cfed6b7115ce1b45ab3c510","tid":2246421,"uid":5298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98d827ad14621ee3ef19db5c669b8bb32e2a777","tid":2246421,"uid":12277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}